    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a rear-mounted M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal traction out of corners. The suspension retains its sharp response thanks to the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system. To ensure long-term mechanical reliability, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the structural integrity and drivetrain synchronization remain excellent, making this a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s last naturally aspirated M flagship.",
