      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a fantastic example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with regular highway use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets and dashboard remain like new. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust and reliable, featuring a complete service log and a recent oil change. It tracks straight, brakes firmly, and the transmission shifts through gears with crisp precision. This is a solid, honest car ready for many more miles of enjoyment.",
